Name: Disruption
Desc: Triggers the disruption of the target's information field and temporarily reduces the shield of enemies with the Equilibrium Field.

Name: Ignition
Desc: The frame's condensed nitrogen has been replaced with a newly created chemical material with an optimized ignition process, making it easier to set the target on fire and deal damage to it over time through attacks.

Name: Ultima Slash
Desc: Adjusts the frame's operation process in battle for an instant output of computing power and launches an extremely powerful attack, dealing damage to the target.

Name: Plasma Beam
Desc: Unleashes powerful energy in a short period to disturb the electrical field of the surroundings. Spreads electric particles to deal damage periodically to the target.

Name: Glaciation
Desc: The cryogenic technology added after multiple iterations of battle modules allows frames to create a small low-temperature area during battle. Further attacks can be unlocked when the parameters in the area reach the preset values over time.

Name: Darkflow
Desc: Using a new type of accelerator technology, it generates and collects dark particles under high pressure, releasing a radiation wave upon reaching critical mass that creates a nullification effect on surrounding targets.

Name: Raydiance
Desc: When plasma is focused by the crystal cluster, the micromitter matrix unleashes it if the electric arc is constrained, producing the "Raydiance" effect, which deals massive damage to targets in a short time.
